text: Chou Tzu-yu (, born June 14, 1999), known mononymously as Tzuyu (, ; ), is a Taiwanese singer. She is based in South Korea. Tzuyu is the youngest member of K-pop girl group TWICE. She is the only Taiwanese member in the group. == References == Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:K-pop singers Category:Taiwanese singers
